column1: 1005:cave. There is a large underground lake in front of you and a draw bridge.:23t:32t:14b:30t:3302:2301:t
1011:cave. There is a large ominous door in front of you. Perhaps it leads to the Duck.:
1014:cave. There is a large waterfall in this chamber. It must come from the underground Lake.:40t:
1015:cave. Large Stalactites hang from the ceiling. Don’t make too much noise!:
1016:cave. This chamber sparkles with Quartz crystals that seem to have sprouted from every wall.:
1017:cave. This chamber appears to be the living quarters for the Duck’s Minions.:42t:
1018:cave. A small stream runs along the side of the tunnel. :33l:40t:
1019:cave. This chamber has large Stalagmites yet no stalactites, how strange.:
1020:cave. This chamber appears to have been transformed into a makeshift Jail.:
1021:cave. This chamber has large columns that extend into a black void above.:
1022:cave on the bridge over the lake.:
